lead_paragraph: The 15 turnovers bothered Michigan State coach Tom Izzo very much. Same for the Spartans' disparity at the line against Northwestern, and a few issues with the shot clock.

headline.print_headline: No. 12 Michigan State Makes 16 3s, Beats Northwestern 76-45
